    <div id="main"> 
     <h2 class="title" id="page-title">Welcome to the Faculty of Law, University of Colombo</h2> 
     <div id="node-1" class="page-ntype published promoted not-sticky full-view author-admin clear-block"> 
      <div class="submitted"> 
      </div> 
      <div class="content"> 
       <div style="TEXT-ALIGN: center">
        <img style="WIDTH: 437px; HEIGHT: 122px" alt="" src="http://www.cmb.ac.lk/academic/law/sites/default/files/front02.jpg" _height="75" _width="75" class="selected ">
       </div> 
       <p align="left"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; FONT-SIZE: 12px"><img style="WIDTH: 420px; HEIGHT: 1px" alt="" src="http://www.cmb.ac.lk/academic/law/sites/default/files/bluani.gif" _height="75" _width="75" height="1" width="459"><br></span></span></p> 
       <div style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; FONT-SIZE: 12px">
        <span style="FONT-SIZE: 12px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; COLOR: #111111; FONT-SIZE: 12px">The Faculty of Law of the University of Colombo is the only Faculty of Law in the entire University system in Sri Lanka. Situated in the heart of Colombo, based within the Island's oldest university, the Faculty of Law offers a four year programme of study, leading to the award of the Bachelor of Laws Degree. In addition, the Faculty of Law also offers courses leading to the Degrees of Master of Laws, Master of Philosophy and Doctor of Philosophy. </span></span>
        <br>
        <span style="FONT-SIZE: 12px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; FONT-SIZE: 12px"></span></span>
        <img style="WIDTH: 419px; HEIGHT: 1px; FONT-SIZE: 12px" alt="" src="http://www.cmb.ac.lk/academic/law/sites/default/files/bluani.gif" _height="75" _width="75" height="1" width="607">
        <br>
        <strong><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; COLOR: #ff7f00; FONT-SIZE: 16px"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial Black">Recent News</span></span></strong>
        <strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><br></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong>
        <br>
        <strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><span style="color: #4040ff;">Commencement of&nbsp; the Academic Year 2014/2015 </span> <p></p></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong>The new academic year for the 2
        <sup>nd </sup>&amp; 3
        <sup>rd</sup> year students and the 2
        <sup>nd</sup> term for&nbsp; the 4
        <sup>th</sup> year students of the Faculty of Law, University of Colombo, commenced on Monday 12
        <sup>th</sup> January 2015.
        <strong><br><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong> <p></p></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong>
       </div> 
       <p><strong><span style="COLOR: #0000ff"></span></strong><a style="COLOR: #0000ff" href="http://www.cmb.ac.lk/academic/law/node/118"><strong><span style="COLOR: #0000ff"></span></strong></a><strong><a style="COLOR: #0000ff" href="http://www.cmb.ac.lk/academic/law/node/119"></a></strong><strong><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12px"></span></strong><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12px"></span></p> 
      </div> 
